as awarded the 2007 <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Nobel_Prize_in_Physics\" title=\"Nobel Prize in Physics\">Nobel Prize in Physics<\/a> together with <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Peter_Gr%C3%BCnberg\" title=\"Peter Gr\u00fcnberg\">Peter Gr\u00fcnberg<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"Albert Fert","place_of_birth":"Carcassonne ,  France","place_of_death":null,"text":"Albert Fert , Physics, 2007","year":2007.0}